Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Mutiple car parks and loading areas

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is delighted to offer 3/1-17 Derrimut Drive, Derrimut for lease.

A prominent corner complex, this warehouse sits on the corner of Boundary Road and Derrimut Drive, at 1-17 Derrimut Drive. 

The property is directly fronting Boundary Road, offering significant signage opportunities for your business (STCA). 

The freeway network is easily accessed via Boundary Road on ramp in Laverton North, or the Robinsons Road on ramp in Derrimut. 

Ample on site parking, a café within the precinct, secure electronic gates and container loading area ensures this property will not last long. 

Key features include:
+ High clearance warehouse
+ On site café
+ Amenities including kitchenette
+ Container height roller door
+ 65 sqm* of fitted first floor office
+ 12 car parks on title

*approx.

CBRE is pleased to present, 30 Grimes Court, Derrimut, for lease. This functional office/warehouse is perfectly designed for any warehousing or logistics occupier. 

Zoned Industrial 2, the property sits only 600m* from Robinsons Road, and only 1km* to the freeway on/off ramp.

Property features includes;
+   Impressive concrete yard – approx. 1,000sqm
+   Massive cubic capacity
+   10m* high internal clearance, allowing to rack 6+ pallets high
+   10m* wide crossover/driveway, allowing ease of access for trucks
+   Motorised sliding gate
+   Two roller doors
+   Three phase power
+   Corporate office and amenities over two levels
+   Ducted heating/cooling

For further information, please contact the CBRE team.

*approx.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: TWO ROLLER DOORS AND 10M* INTERNAL CLEARANCE

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
26 Radnor Drive, Deer Park is a property which offers the perfect blend of office, retail showroom and high clearance warehouse. It is an ‘all in one’ concept for your corporate headquarters, distribution centre and retail offering. 

The Paramount Industrial Estate offers a blend of logistical benefits and local amenity. Highlights include nearby Deer Park Train Station (800m) and a large scale commercial/retail strip on Mt Derrimut Road. With a business in this location, your operation will benefit by the proximity to the Port of Melbourne and freeways. Additionally, your staff and customers will be attracted to public transport routes and neighbouring food and retail amenity. This is certainly not a typical building in an industrial estate.

Key building highlights include the following:
+ Massive cubic capacity – 9m* high internal clearance
+ Clear span warehouse 
+ Container height motorised roller door
+ Full load bearing mezzanine level in addition to office
+ Ground floor showroom with ability to customise
+ Corporate office over two levels 
+ Heating/cooling
+ Multiple bathrooms and kitchenettes
+ Modern façade and landscaping
+ 20 allocated car parks
+ Three phase power
+ Racking plan available on request

*approx.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: A-GRADE WAREHOUSE WITH RETAIL SHOWROOM AND CORPORATE OFFICE
